@@TJvCaptionButton.Action
Summary
  Designates the action associated with the caption button.
Description
  Action designates the action object that is associated with the caption button. Actions allow an
  application to centralize the response to user commands. When a control is associated with an action,
  the action determines the appropriate properties and events of the control (such as whether the
  control is enabled or how it responds to an OnClick event).

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCaptionButton.ActionLink
Summary
  Contains the action link object associated with the caption button.
Description
  ActionLink handles the association between the button and the action specified by the Action
  property. The action link determines which properties and events of the action object determine the
  values of corresponding properties and events of the caption button.
See Also
  TJvCaptionButton.Action

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCaptionButton.Alignment
Summary
