@@TJvCaptionButton.Standard
Summary
  Determines the type of caption button.
Description
  Standard determines the type of caption button to use. When set to tsbNone, it is a custom button
  with a custom text (specified by Caption) and image (specified by ImageIndex and Images).

  Otherwise it's a standard button, such as a Minimize or Close caption button in the way it is
